Q.1>Write a Python program to perform union, intersection and difference operations on set A and Set B
 Code-
set_a = set(map(int, input("Set A: ").split()))


set_b = set(map(int, input("Set B: ").split()))


union_set = set_a | set_b # Union
intersection_set = set_a & set_b # Intersection
difference_set = set_a - set_b # Difference (A - B)

print("Union:", union_set)
print("Intersection:", intersection_set)
print("Difference:", difference_set)
